Detailed Description

Collection of Springs.

vtkSpringCollection represents and provides methods to manipulate a list of Springs (i.e., vtkSpring and subclasses). The list is unsorted and duplicate entries are not prevented.

See also:
vtkCollection, vtkSpring

vtkSpring * vtkSpringCollection::GetNextSpring (  ) 

Return the next Spring on the list.

Get the Spring at the pointer position. Beware of calling InitTraversal() to init the pointer. NULL is returned when the collection is exhausted.
